  "date": "2017-10-03",
  "title": "Hash Power - Part 2",
  "t": "Crypto isn't currency, it's commodity-like asset class with a twist: the token actually does work (unlike gold). Traditional valuation models (revenue multiples, P/E) don't apply.",
